# Scope
- React 18+ with TypeScript for all UI components
- shadcn/ui component library integration
- Reusable components (especially DataTable)
- Centralized API communication via src/lib/api.ts

# Non-goals
- No direct Graph API calls from frontend code
- No custom UI component library development (use shadcn/ui)
- No jQuery or legacy frontend frameworks
- No server-side rendering (SSR) for MVP

# Standards
- React + shadcn/ui.
- Reusable <DataTable/>.
- Fetch only via src/lib/api.ts.
- No direct Graph calls in frontend.
